episodes.title: 29 KOJC members face charges as 60 cops injured in Quiboloy hunt
episodes.description:
#OneNewsNow | At least 29 Kingdom of Jesus Christ (KOJC) members face charges after 60 police officers were injured during the execution of an arrest warrant for pastor Apollo Quiboloy. | via #MOJO Evan Tarinque

episodes.title: PNP detects possible underground bunker in KOJC Compound, intensifies search for Apollo Quiboloy
episodes.description:
#TheBigStory | PNP Spokesperson Col. Jean Fajardo said that the PNP believes Apollo Quiboloy and other accused individuals are inside the KOJC compound, with ground-penetrating radar detecting heartbeats 20-30 meters underground, leading to a focused search for the bunker’s entrance.
